<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>당신이 이성계라면? — 의리의 왕</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --bg:#0a0604;--bg2:#0f0906;--bg3:#140c08;
  --gold2:#8a5e1a;--gold3:#e0b060;
  --text:#ece0d0;--text2:#c8b89a;--text3:#907860;
  --border:#1e1408;--border2:#2e1e0c;--border3:#4e3418;
  --green2:#208848;--green3:#70f080;
  --red2:#803020;--red3:#f07060;
  --hist2:#3a2808;--hist3:#c09040;
}

/* ── 기본 ── */
html{background:var(--bg);}
html,body{min-height:100%;}
body{font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;min-height:100vh;}

/* ── 씬 ──
   모든 씬은 display:none/flex로만 전환
   position:fixed 없음 → 창 크기에 무관하게 동작
   min-height:100vh → 내용 짧아도 전체 화면 채움
   overflow:visible → 내용 길어지면 자연스럽게 스크롤
*/
.sc{
  display:none;
  flex-direction:column;
  min-height:100vh;
  background:var(--bg);
  opacity:0;
  transition:opacity 0.35s ease;
}
.sc.on{display:flex;}

@keyframes fi{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
@keyframes fi-up{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* ── 진행바 ── */
.prog{flex-shrink:0;background:var(--bg);padding:8px 20px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;}
.prog-bar{flex:1;height:2px;background:var(--border2);border-radius:1px;overflow:hidden;}
.prog-fill{height:100%;background:var(--gold2);transition:width .6s ease;}
.prog-lbl{font-size:11px;color:#c0a060;letter-spacing:1px;white-space:nowrap;}

/* ── 아트 ── */
.art{flex-shrink:0;background:#060402;}
.art svg{width:100%;display:block;}

/* ── 나레이션 ── */
.narr-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:40px 28px;}
.narr-era{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;color:#a08060;margin-bottom:18px;}
.narr-text{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:20px;line-height:2.8;color:var(--text2);}
.narr-text em{color:var(--text);font-style:normal;}
.cursor{display:inline-block;width:2px;height:1em;background:#c08040;margin-left:2px;vertical-align:text-bottom;animation:blink .7s step-end infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}
.nav-area{flex-shrink:0;padding:16px 24px 32px;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

/* ── 시대상황 ── */
.context-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:32px 28px;}
.ctx-year{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:700;color:#6a4020;line-height:1;margin-bottom:20px;}
.ctx-title{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:.5px;}
.ctx-body{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2.3;}
.ctx-body strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:400;}

/* ── 게임 ── */
.game-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:20px 24px 0;}
.dial-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.dial{border-radius:6px;padding:13px 16px;animation:fi-up .3s ease;}
.dial.npc-left{background:#0f0804;border:1px solid #2a1808;border-left:2px solid #c07840;}
.dial.npc-right{background:#080e04;border:1px solid #141e08;border-left:2px solid #608828;}
.dial.npc-mid{background:#0a080e;border:1px solid #1a1428;border-left:2px solid #806890;}
.dial.king{background:#0a0804;border:1px solid #1e1408;border-left:2px solid #907030;}
.dial-who{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px;}
.dial.npc-left .dial-who{color:#c87840;}
.dial.npc-right .dial-who{color:#80a848;}
.dial.npc-mid .dial-who{color:#9878b8;}
.dial.king .dial-who{color:#b09050;}
.dial-text{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);line-height:2;}
.inner-voice{margin:0 0 14px;padding:11px 15px;border-left:2px solid #3a2808;background:#080604;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:13px;color:#907050;line-height:2.1;font-style:italic;animation:fi .4s ease;}

.ch-area{padding:16px 0 32px;}
.ch-label{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:14px;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;letter-spacing:.3px;line-height:1.6;}
.ch-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;}
.ch{width:100%;text-align:left;background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;padding:13px 15px;color:var(--text2);font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.ch:hover:not(.iseonggye):not(.blocked){background:#140e08;border-color:var(--border3);color:var(--text);}
.ch.iseonggye{background:#180e04;border-color:var(--hist2);color:var(--hist3);cursor:default;}
.ch.blocked{opacity:.25;cursor:default;pointer-events:none;}
.ch.wrong-shake{animation:shake .35s ease;}
@keyframes shake{0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)}25%{transform:translateX(-6px)}75%{transform:translateX(6px)}}

.block-msg{display:none;margin-top:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:#0e0806;border:1px solid #503010;border-radius:5px;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:13px;color:#a07040;line-height:1.8;animation:fi .3s ease;}
.block-msg.on{display:block;}

/* 4막 정답없음 */
.no-answer-msg{display:none;margin-top:10px;padding:12px 16px;background:#0e0a06;border:1px solid var(--border3);border-radius:5px;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2;animation:fi .3s ease;}
.no-answer-msg.on{display:block;}
.no-answer-nav{display:none;margin-top:12px;}
.no-answer-nav.on{display:flex;gap:8px;}

/* ── 깊게살펴보기 ── */
.deep-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:28px 24px;}
.deep-tag{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--gold3);}
.deep-title{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;}
.deep-text{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2.3;}
.deep-text em{color:var(--text3);font-style:italic;}
.deep-quote{margin-top:16px;padding:12px 16px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold2);background:#0c0804;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:13px;color:#c0a060;line-height:2;font-style:italic;}

/* ── 오프닝 ── */
.opening{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:40px 28px;text-align:center;}
.op-question{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0;letter-spacing:.5px;line-height:2;}
.op-glyph{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#604020;line-height:1;margin-bottom:18px;opacity:0;}
.op-series{font-size:11px;color:#c0a060;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:28px;opacity:0;}
.op-stage{position:relative;width:100%;height:90px;margin-bottom:28px;}
.op-line{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:100%;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2.6;opacity:0;transition:opacity 1.4s ease;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:4px;}
.op-line em{color:var(--gold3);font-style:normal;}
.op-disc{font-size:12px;color:#c0a060;margin-top:14px;line-height:1.9;opacity:0;}

/* ── 환생 ── */
.rebirth{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:40px 28px;}
.rb-portal-wrap{width:100px;height:100px;margin:0 auto 36px;}
.rb-portal{width:100px;height:100px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;transition:opacity 1s ease;position:relative;}
.rb-portal.show{opacity:1;}
.rb-ring-out{position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid transparent;border-top:1.5px solid var(--gold2);border-right:1.5px solid var(--gold2);}
.rb-portal.show .rb-ring-out{animation:spin 2s linear infinite;}
.rb-ring-mid{position:absolute;inset:14px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid transparent;border-bottom:1px solid #c07830;border-left:1px solid #c07830;}
.rb-portal.show .rb-ring-mid{animation:spin 1.4s linear infinite reverse;}
.rb-glyph{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold2);opacity:0;transition:opacity 1.2s ease .3s;}
.rb-portal.show .rb-glyph{opacity:1;}
@keyframes spin{from{transform:rotate(0)}to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.rb-stage{position:relative;width:100%;height:68px;margin-bottom:36px;}
.rb-word{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);white-space:nowrap;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--text2);opacity:0;transition:opacity .9s ease;}
.rb-word.dim{font-size:15px;color:#504030;}
.rb-word.final{font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:1px;}
#rb-cta{opacity:0;transition:opacity 1s ease;}

/* ── 에필로그 ── */
.epi-body{flex:1;padding:28px;}
.epi-year{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;color:#c0a060;margin-bottom:12px;}
.epi-big{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;}
.epi-text{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2.2;margin-bottom:14px;}
.epi-quote{padding:12px 18px;border-top:1px solid var(--border3);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border3);font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold3);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:14px;}

/* ── 공통 버튼 ── */
.btn-p{padding:11px 24px;border-radius:22px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;transition:all .2s;background:#0c0806;border:1px solid #3a2008;color:#c09040;}
.btn-p:hover{background:#160e06;border-color:var(--gold3);}
.btn-s{padding:11px 24px;border-radius:22px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;transition:all .2s;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border3);color:var(--text3);}
.btn-s:hover{border-color:#604828;color:var(--text2);}

/* ── 메뉴 ── */
.menu-wrap{position:fixed;top:12px;right:12px;z-index:400;}
.menu-btn{background:rgba(10,6,4,.92);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1;transition:color .2s;}
.menu-btn:hover{color:var(--text);}
.menu-drop{display:none;position:absolute;top:34px;right:0;background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;min-width:160px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.7);}
.menu-drop.open{display:block;animation:fi-up .2s ease;}
.menu-item{display:block;width:100%;text-align:left;padding:10px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .15s;}
.menu-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.menu-item:hover{background:#140e08;color:var(--text);}
.menu-divider{height:1px;background:var(--border2);margin:2px 0;}
.menu-section{padding:6px 16px 3px;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--text3);}

/* ── 퀴즈 ── */
.quiz-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:20px 24px 32px;gap:0;}
.quiz-num{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:8px;}
.quiz-question{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:16px;}
.quiz-choices{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;}
.quiz-timer{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);}

/* ── 후기 ── */
.rv-title{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;}
.rv-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.8;}
.rv-input{width:100%;background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px;display:block;}
.rv-textarea{width:100%;background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;resize:none;height:110px;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:8px;display:block;}
.rv-input:focus,.rv-textarea:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--border3);}
.rv-sent{display:none;padding:14px;background:#0c0e08;border:1px solid #303a18;border-radius:6px;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:#90a858;text-align:center;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ■ 씬 0: 오프닝 -->
<div class="sc on" id="s0">
<div class="opening">
  <div class="op-question" id="op-question">왕명을 따르면 내 사람을 잃는다.<br>따르지 않아도 내 사람을 잃는다.<br>따를 것인가. 따르지 않을 것인가. 선택하라.</div>
  <div class="op-glyph" id="op-glyph">朝</div>
  <div class="op-series" id="op-series">역사체험 교육 게임 · 조선의 왕 시리즈 1화</div>

  <!-- 5초 선택 구역 — 오프닝에서 바로 등장 -->
  <div id="op-choice-area" style="width:100%;opacity:0;transition:opacity .8s ease;">
    <!-- 숫자 카운트다운 -->
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <span id="op-timer-num" style="font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold3);line-height:1;">5</span>
    </div>
    <!-- 두 선택지 -->
    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;">
      <button id="op-btn-follow" onclick="opChoose('follow')" style="flex:1;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--text2);background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;padding:16px 10px;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.8;transition:all .15s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#160e06';this.style.borderColor='var(--gold3)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#0a0806';this.style.borderColor='var(--border2)'">① 따른다</button>
      <button id="op-btn-defy" onclick="opChoose('defy')" style="flex:1;font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--text2);background:#0a0806;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;padding:16px 10px;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.8;transition:all .15s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#160e06';this.style.borderColor='var(--gold3)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#0a0806';this.style.borderColor='var(--border2)'">② 따르지 않는다</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="op-disc" id="op-disc"><strong>※ 역사적 사실을 바탕으로 한 교육 목적의 재구성입니다.</strong></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ■ 씬 1: 환생 -->
<div class="sc" id="s1">
<div class="rebirth">
  <div class="rb-portal-wrap">
    <div class="rb-portal" id="rb-portal">
      <div class="rb-ring-out"></div><div class="rb-ring-mid"></div>
      <div class="rb-glyph">朝</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="rb-stage" id="rb-stage"></div>
  <div id="rb-cta">
    <button onclick="go(2)" style="font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;font-size:14px;color:#d09840;background:#0c0804;border:1px solid #3a2008;padding:11px 36px;border-radius:2px;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:2px;">들어간다</button>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
     0막 — 때를 기다린다
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- ■ 씬 2: 0막 나레이션 -->
<div class="sc" id="s2">
<div class="art" style="height:150px;">
<svg viewBox="0 0 640 150" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <rect width="640" height="150" fill="#060402"/>
  <rect x="0" y="100" width="640" height="50" fill="#040302"/>
  <path d="M0 108 Q80 98 160 108 Q240 118 320 106 Q400 94 480 106 Q560 118 640 108" stroke="#1a0e06" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
  <!-- 아버지와 이성계 실루엣 -->
  <circle cx="280" cy="80" r="8" fill="#5a3a18"/><rect x="272" y="88" width="16" height="22" fill="#5a3a18" rx="2"/>
  <circle cx="320" cy="84" r="7" fill="#4a2e10"/><rect x="313" y="91" width="14" height="20" fill="#4a2e10" rx="2"/>
  <!-- 횃불 -->
  <rect x="360" y="72" width="4" height="30" fill="#6a3a14"/>
  <ellipse cx="362" cy="70" rx="6" ry="8" fill="#e07030" opacity=".9"/>
  <ellipse cx="362" cy="68" rx="4" ry="6" fill="#f0c050" opacity=".7"/>
  <!-- 산 실루엣 -->
  <path d="M0 150 Q60 80 120 110 Q180 80 240 150" fill="#2a1a0a" opacity=".9"/>
  <path d="M420 150 Q500 70 560 100 Q600 80 640 150" fill="#2a1a0a" opacity=".9"/>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="narr-body">
  <div class="narr-era">0막 · 1356년</div>
  <div class="narr-text" id="narr2"></div>
</div>
<div class="nav-area" id="nav2" style="display:none;">
  <button class="btn-p" onclick="go(3)">시대 상황 보기 →</button>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ■ 씬 3: 0막 시대상황 -->
<div class="sc scrollable" id="s3">
<div class="context-body">
  <div class="ctx-year">1356</div>
  <div class="ctx-title">흔들리는 나라 — 차별이 시작됐다</div>
  <div class="ctx-body">
    이성계의 집안은 함경도 쌍성의 실력자였습니다. 토박이 호족으로 삶은 팍팍하지 않았습니다.<br><br>
    그런데 원나라 황실이 권력 싸움에 빠졌습니다. 1340년대 가뭄과 홍수가 연이어 왔습니다. 백성들이 반란을 일으켰습니다. 원나라가 흔들렸습니다.<br><br>
    고려 이주민의 차별이 점차 심해지고 있습니다.<br><br>
    아버지의 동료들이 싸웠습니다. 크게 다쳤습니다. 싸움에서 이겼지만 더 큰 원나라 병사들이 왔습니다. 동료들은 아버지를 원망했습니다. 아버지는 대답하지 않았습니다.
  </div>
</div>
<div class="nav-area">
  <button class="btn-p" onclick="go(4)">게임 시작 →</button>
  <button class="btn-s" onclick="go(4)">건너뛰기</button>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ■ 씬 4: 0막 게임 -->
<div class="sc" id="s4">
<div class="prog"><div class="prog-bar"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:14%"></div></div><span class="prog-lbl">0막 · 1356년</span></div>
<div class="game-body">
  <div class="dial-wrap">
    <div class="dial npc-left">
      <div class="dial-who">아버지의 동료</div>
      <div class="dial-text">"동료들이 다쳤소. 함께 싸웠다면 달랐을 거요. 당신은 왜 움직이지 않았소?"</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ch-area">
    <div class="ch-label">지금 싸우시겠습니까?</div>
    <div class="ch-list">
      <button class="ch" id="g4a" onclick="tryPick(4,'a','x')">① 싸운다</button>
